About this item

  • 【Universal Compatibility】:Our dual-port USB C PD 36w fast charger and dual USB C to USB C charging cable are widely compatible with ipad 9 generation charger, 2022/2021/2020/2018 I Pad Pro 12.9 in 5th/4th/3rd generation, I Pad Pro 11 in 3rd/2nd/1st generation (2021/2020/2018), I Pad mini 6(2021), I Pad Air 4(2020), I Pad
  • 【36W Dual USB-C Fast Charger】: The PD 36W fast charger uses our built-in USB C to USB C cable to quickly charge the i Phone 15 or i Pad air from 0% to 50% in 25 minutes. When only one port is working, it is ultra fast charging (up to 36W), while when two ports are working simultaneously, it is fast charging (up to 18-20W).
  • 【Small Size Big Power】:The size of this charger is almost the same as the 20W charger block. The 2-port portable charging block is compact and lightweight for breakthrough performance. It can withstand bumps, drops and falls and is durable. It is easy to carry around and ideal for home, office and on the go.
  • 【USB C to C Cable 2m 】:Our 36w fast charger plug with 2m USB C to USB C cable. The USB C to USB C cable supports 480Mbps data synchronization. You will like the length, which allows you to work at greater distances and charge devices such as iPad or Samsung while on the move.
  • 【What You Get】: After purchasing, you will get: 2 pcs dual port Type C fast charging block and 2m c to c fast data cable, and our friendly customer service. If you have any questions, please contact us.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Melanie
4.0 out of 5 stars Supercharging The GALAXY S23+
Reviewed in the United States on August 20, 2024
Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
I purchased this charger for my Samsung Galaxy S23+, and overall, I'm very satisfied with it. When only my phone is connected, it provides super charging, which gets my phone to full in about 30 minutes, or 45 minutes if the battery is very low. When I connect two devices, they both fast charge, but not at super charging speed. In that case, it takes about an hour for my phone to reach full charge, which is still pretty quick.

The charger comes with two separate Type-C charging blocks, each capable of charging two devices simultaneously, and it includes two Type-C to Type-C cords. The cords are a decent length, allowing me to comfortably use my phone in bed without being tethered too closely to the charger. However, they are a bit stiff out of the box due to being shipped with ties, so it might take some time for them to relax. I do wish they were a bit more flexible.

One minor downside is that while the charging blocks can handle two devices each, only two cords are included. Since I don't have spare Type-C to Type-C cables lying around, I can't fully use both blocks until I purchase additional cords.

Overall, this was a great purchase, and I’d recommend it to anyone looking for a reliable and fast charger, especially for Samsung devices.

Hans
5.0 out of 5 stars As described, though unable to test the 36W claim, and doesn't support Samsung Super Fast charging
Reviewed in the United States on August 17, 2024
Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
This charger satisfied my requirement of a two-port USB-Charger so I could charge my phone and my galaxy watch at the same time while in a hotel. This charger does that, though at standard fast charging speeds. That's just fine for overnight on my hotel bedside table.

The watch charges as fast as it would on the Samsung charger but my phone is capable of super fast charging from a Samsung charger. This one is unable to do it even though the requirement should just be PD charging. It's not the cable; I tried one of the included cables on the Samsung charger and it worked as expected. That said, nowhere in the description does it say that it supports Samsung 'super fast charging' (only that it's Samsung compatible, which it is) so I'm reluctant to ding a star for that.

The cables do pass data as described. Overall this is a great value for what you get (two chargers and two cables). You forego only the very fastest charging speeds (at least on Samsung devices).

Overall i'm pleased to have solved my charging needs while traveling. I suspect that Apple users will be even more satisifed.
